#

Grilled Chicken Burrito with Avocado Salsa

$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyWheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BurritoMexicanGrilled ChickenHealthy

Description

A hearty grilled chicken burrito stuffed with fresh vegetables and topped with creamy avocado salsa, delivering a satisfying and delicious meal.

Ingredients

  • Grilled Chicken Breast: 200g
  • Flour Tortilla: 1 large
  • Avocado: 1 ripe
  • Roma Tomatoes: 2 diced
  • Red Onion: 1/4 diced
  • Lime Juice: 1 tbsp
  • Cilantro: 2 tbsp chopped
  • Sour Cream: 2 tbsp
  • Shredded Cheese: 1/4 cup
